<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n54121h"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n54" href="#n54121h">N54 (VI.B.45)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n54all.htm#n54121h"> 121(h)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> not / leave tragic place: ~ <small>Orange</small></blockquote> <dd class="well"> <ul class="list-inline" id="n54121h"> <li>FW unlocated</li> </ul> <blockquote class="sources">&ldquo;My mother&apos;s brother, and my husband were killed here by a ferocious tiger;&rdquo; she said, &ldquo;and now my son has met the same fate.&rdquo; <p>&ldquo;Why do you <mark>not move away from such a dangerous neighborhood?</mark>&rdquo; inquired the disciple.</p> <p>&ldquo;But the officials here are not oppressive,&rdquo; the woman explained&rsquo;</p> <p>Master Kung was told of the incident and said to his discipes:</p> <p>&ldquo;You hear that, my children! An oppressive official is more to be feared than a dangerous tiger.&rdquo;</p> <small> Carl Crow, <a name="CCMK" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#CCMK"><cite title="source">Master Kung. The Story of Confucius</cite></a> (Sep 1937) 123</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
